{"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"location is being tracked.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two foci"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically, this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property has no effect if the "},{"code":"userTrackingMode","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value other than "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view with an animated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"transition. If you don’t want to animate the change, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L752"},"title":"targetCoordinate","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)targetCoordinate","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","role":"collecti